add table ip6 ferm
delete table ip6 ferm
add table ip6 ferm
add chain ip6 ferm INPUT { type filter hook input priority 0; }
add rule ip6 ferm INPUT tcp dport 22 reject with icmpv6 type policy-fail
add rule ip6 ferm INPUT tcp dport 23 reject with icmpv6 type reject-route
add rule ip6 ferm INPUT tcp dport 24 reject with icmpv6 type port-unreachable
